# Save output options in your YAML

.pull-left[

```{r echo = FALSE}
yml_empty() %>% 
  yml_output(html_document()) %>% 
  asis_yaml_output()
```

```{r echo = FALSE}
yml_empty() %>% 
  yml_output(html_document(toc = TRUE)) %>% 
  asis_yaml_output()
```


]

