# Answers

```{r echo = FALSE}
yml_empty() %>% 
  yml_output(html_document(toc = TRUE,
                           toc_float = TRUE,
                           theme = "flatly",
                           df_print = "kable",
                           code_download = TRUE)) %>% 
  asis_yaml_output()
```

