# Pop quiz

--

.pull-left[

How do you add headers in Markdown?

`! Header`

`- Header`

`# Header`

`1. Header`

]

--

.pull-right[

What about lists? Bulleted? Numbered?

`! Item 1`

`- Item 1`

`# Item 1`

`1. Item 1`

]

